    "Camera systems and ADAS that reduce blind spots, on the other hand, have been met with approval by truck drivers (33).",
    "Still, which ADAS are perceived by truck drivers as useful and which as less useful has not yet been well documented in the literature.",
    "Although certain pain points in the trucking industry have been documented [e.g., tight schedules, stress, and fatigue (34) (35) (36) (37) ], there is still limited knowledge about how truck drivers experience their daily work.",
    "This is particularly relevant in recent years, as factors such as driver shortages (38) and the introduction of new technologies are playing increasingly large roles.",
    "The aim of this study is to document the experiences of Dutch truck drivers."
  ],
